Cleaning of LMAO

Removal of unused lib files and useless code.
add songs and edit all scripts to work

BPM displayed

On the scoring circle
Addtion of MP3 Lib and minor adjustments

Edited ChangingBPMWithHand.html

Ive edited the variable names to make maintenance easier. I have also
included a function to make sure that prior to the hand being detected
by the leap motion machine,  the song will play at the original bpm.
Only after hand has been detected once that bpm will be 0 if hand is
taken away from the leap motion.

Deleted index.html & added new code

I edited my ChangingBPMWithHand.html to run using setInterval instead of
controller.on to add compatibility with Matthias' and ML's code.

Addition of GUI

Basic GUI system

JS LeapMotion API

Added the API library.

Change BPM with palm velocity

This file will change the BPM of the song based on the palm velocity.
I propose we use the BPM integer value to determine the song file with the suitable speed to be played
